        public SpatialSparseVertex addVertex(SpatialSparseGraph graph,
                                     com.vividsolutions.jts.geom.Point point)
        Creates and adds a new vertex to a graph. The spatial reference id of point will be set to the one of the builders spatial reference system.
        Parameters:
        graph - the graph a new vertex should be inserted in.
        point - the point in space where the vertex is located.
        Returns:
        the newly inserted vertex, or null is the insertion of a vertex would violate the definition of the underlying graph.
